Watch me turn my thin lips into plump lips using only two products💋 #complimentaryfrombuxom 
.
This lip kit completely transforms my lips in seconds and I especially love these two shades together. I’m using Smooth Spice Power Line plumping liner and Catching Rays in the Full On plumping matte lip from @buxomcosmetics

This is the only way I will like my lips from now on because it’s so much easier than just over lining. Make a line down the middle going over the natural lip line. So fast & so easy to create full lips that last all day 💋

social_posts.post_text:
Batch Microcreamery at The Promenade grand opening was a major success yesterday! The weather was rainy and chilly and yet the joint was packed all day long. So proud of my friends for their third location opening! The ice cream nachos were a dream. Three scoops of my choosing (I went with birthday cake, chocolate, pistachio) with three topping choices (rainbow sprinkles, whipped cream, three cherries) over waffle cone chips. Perfect treat to share with your buddy 😉 
.
When the weather is less rainy, take a load off right outside their door at the fire pit and lounge chairs. Can’t wait to visit again soon, especially this summer!
.
#lehighvalley #bethlehempa #supportlocalbusiness #icecreamlove

Spring styling with a 70s spin ✌🏼 
This time of year is so tricky to dress for. Chilly mornings. Warm, sunny afternoons. Brisk evenings. Scattered showers. The key is layers and anticipating the worst. This weekend was chill and spent mostly at home with the fam. We ate yummy food and watched Harry Potter. Love weekends dedicated to recharging the body and mind. Spring is my favorite time of year because it’s the beginning of a fresh start. Anyone else think spring is their favorite season?
.

Love doing a slicked back bun for a daytime, clean girl look. As a stay at home mom, I want to look polished but not spend too much time on my hair and makeup. While I see a lot of girls use hair gel, I prefer using a deep conditioner to achieve the same look that also treats my hair. Here I’m using the @randco High Dive at the base and @theouai hair oil for the ends. If I could bathe in this oil I would, guys, this scent is pure heaven. My hair seriously just sucks this stuff up and feels so thick and luxurious the next day after a blowout. Lip stain so i can have my overlined lips all day without reapplying, brushed up brows and sheer eye balm on my lids give the put together, effortless look I want. Missing the cruiser life with my bar stool buddy 💋🍹
.
Patrick and I were married seven years ago and have never gone on a proper honeymoon. We went to Cape May for a few days after the wedding and planned on something bigger a few months later when the winter blues hit. But shortly after getting hitched, we found out that I was expecting our little Lucy and plans changed lol. Since then, anytime we went away together was for a wedding or business trip or with friends. Never alone and never for more than a few days. Finally going away together without any other reason but to enjoy each others company was truly amazing. The cruise life might just be for us but next time, we’re bringing the girlies ♥️ 
I’m not sure when we’ll have an opportunity again where it’s just us away together but that’s ok. I’ll savor these memories under the sun with white sandy beaches and crystal clear water. Sitting at the tiki bar making friends and laughing over silly inside jokes only we think are funny. Until next time, bon voyage 👋🏼 🛥️
